metadata.name: Dead Decor #1
metadata.description:
Dead Decor is a collection of 500 unique backgrounds, made using a selection of 27 custom made items. The focus of this project is to bring additional character and customisation to your profile picture. Inspired by the Fellaz, but open to all!

If you have a fella, you can add it to your room at [deaddecor.co](https://deaddecor.co/).

If you have a different pfp, you can download your room with a transparent background [here](https://deaddecor.co/download/room/1).
